msgctxt "StorageNetwork.STRINGS.UI.STORAGE_NETWORK.CONFIG_RESTART_REQUIRED"
msgid "要使这些选项生效，必须重新启动游戏。"
msgstr "The game must be restarted for these options to take effect."

